flowchart TD
    A[User selects Excel] --> B[openpyxl loads workbook]
    B --> C{Hoja1 exists?}
    C -- yes --> D[Use Hoja1]
    C -- no --> E[Fallback to active sheet]
    D --> F[Map header row]
    E --> F
    F --> G[Read asset id, description, section]
    B --> H[Read anchored images]
    H --> I[Map image by anchor row]
    G --> J[Create AssetRecord per row]
    I --> J
    J --> K[Emit records and filters]
